 and get AI writing help.",improveText:window.RDL.Localization.enhanceWithAIbtn||"Enhance with AI",headingText:window.RDL.Localization.headingText||"Highlight a bullet point, then click here to enhance clarity with AI.",flyOutCtaText:window.RDL.Localization.flyOutCtaText||"Got It",flyOutInstructions_1:window.RDL.Localization.flyOutInstructions_1||"Highlight a full bullet point of text",flyOutInstructions_2:window.RDL.Localization.flyOutInstructions_2||"Click the button <em>‘Enhance with AI’<em>",flyOutInstructions_3:window.RDL.Localization.flyOutInstructions_3||"View the results, make edits"},ttcRephraseAiModal:{title:window.RDL.Localization.ttcRephraseAiModaltitle||"Here are a few options for AI enhanced grammar,<br/>clarity and readability."},ttcRephraseErrModal:{description:"TTC Rephrase AI Modal Error",noResult:{title:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalNoresultTitle||"We experienced an error fetching AI suggestions",desc:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalNoresultDesc||"Our AI helper is experiencing some issues. Please, click “Try again” below and give it another shot. Or close out and try again later.",primaryCTAText:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalNoresultPrimaryCTA||"Try again",secondaryCTAText:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalNoresultSecondaryCTA||"Cancel"},apiError:{title:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalApiErrortTitle||"Our AI helper is currently down. Please try again later.",desc:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalApiErrortDesc||"We apologize for the inconvenience. Our AI helper is currently undergoing maintenance. We'll have it back up as soon as possible.",primaryCTAText:window.RDL.Localization.ttcErrorModalApiErrortPrimaryCTA||"Got it"}}}},Hi={trustScore:"4.4",numberOfReviews:"8,469"},ji={promotingText:window.RDL.Localization.summPromotingText,genSummBannerHeader:window.RDL.Localization.genSummBannerHeader,genSummaryCTAText1:window.RDL.Localization.genSummaryCTAText1,genSummaryCTAText2:window.RDL.Localization.genSummaryCTAText2,genS