mplate</span>",popupTitleV2:"3 simple questions to your <br/>perfect template",colorPickerTitle:"Pick a color",choosePhotoOptTitle:"Do you want to include your photo?",choosePhotoOptSubTitle:"This is standard practice in some regions and industries.",noPhotoTitle:"No photo",photoTitle:"Photo",chooseColumnTitle:"Which layout do you prefer?",chooseColumnSubTitle:"One column saves space; two columns look modern and organized.",oneColumnTitle:"One column",twoColumnTitle:"Two columns",chooseFieldTitle:"What field is this resume for?",chooseFieldSubTitle:"Check all that apply or skip.",colorPickerSubTitle:"We'll use this to accent your resume—change colors anytime.",popupDesc:"Get recommendations to match your style, field, and career goals.",popupDescV2:"First, let’s pick a color—we’ll use this to accent your resume.",seeMyBtn:"See my results",noThanksBtn:"No thanks",letsGoBtn:"Let’s go"},Xa={mainHead:"Upload your resume",mainDesc:"Even if you think it's outdated, uploading your existing resume makes it easier and faster to edit and customize.",drapNDrop:"Drag & drop your file here or",btnbrowser:"Browse",SemFlowH1:"Do you have a resume we can use to get started?",btnDropBox:"Upload from Dropbox",btnGoogleDrive:"Upload from Google Drive",acceptableFiles:window.RDL.Localization.acceptableFiles,acceptableFilesType:window.RDL.Localization.acceptableFilesType,startScratchText:"Want to start from scratch?",createNewResume:window.RDL.Localization.resumeFromScratchTitle,btnUpload:window.RDL.Localization.btnUpload,uploadFormatErrorICTA:window.RDL.Localization.uploadFormatErrorICTA,changeFile:"Change file"},qa={updateEducation:"Update your education"},Ya=["driver","cashier","server","forklift operator","babysitter","warehouse worker","security officer","home health aide","caregiver","machine operator","volunteer","receptionist","front desk receptionist","medical assistant","delivery driver","cook","barista","housekeeper","laborer","line cook","certified nursing assistant","production worker","material handler","warehouse associate","maintenance technician","package handler","office manager","store manager","lifeguard","dental assistant","dishwasher","cleaner","welder","laboratory technician","restaurant busser","front of house employee","barber"],Qa={title:"Enhance your resume with our premium tools",subtitle:"What would you like to do next?",changeTemplateBtn:"Change<br/> Template",adjustFormattingBtn:"Adjust<br/> Formatting",addEditSectionBtn:"Add or Edit<br/> Sections",changeTemplateAndFormatBtn:"Change Template<br/> & Format",enhanceWithAiBtn:"Enhance<br/> with AI",tooltipCloseBtn:"Got It",tooltipTitleChangeTemplate:"Change template",tooltipSubTitleChangeTemplate:"Choose a template from the options below.",tooltipTitleAdjustFormat:"Adjust formatting",tooltipSubTitleAdjustFormat:"Use the formatting tools in this menu to make sure your resume looks good.",tooltipTitleAddEditSection:"Add or edit sections",tooltipSubTitleAddEditSection:"Include sections in your resume by clicking “+”, and make edits.",tooltipTitleChangeTemplateAndFormat:"Change template & format",tooltipSubTitleChangeTemplateAndFormat:"Choose a template from this menu, and use our formatting tools to enhance your resume.",tooltipTitleEnhanceWithAi:"Enhance with AI",tooltipSubTitleEnhanceWithAi:"Get impressive results with AI!<br/> Improve a section (Experience, Skills or Summary), by using the AI button to enhance clarity.",tooltipTitleAddSection:"Add a section",tooltipSubTitleAddSection:"Add a section to include  more accomplishments & highlights.",tooltipTitleResumeCheck:"Resume check",tooltipSubTitleResumeCheck:"Check your resume for score and errors."},$a={ADD_SECTION:"ADDSECTION",TEMPLATE:"TEMPLATE",FORMATTING:"FORMATTING"},er={lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_education:"You may notice a gap in my employment while reviewing my resume. During this period, I elected to take a leave from the workforce in order to go back to school. The time that I was able to commit to my education has been invaluable to my professional growth, and I am eager to re-enter the professional sphere and apply my newfound qualifications and knowledge to the job.",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_family:"I have been out of the field for a time due to some unexpected medical issues. Everything has been taken care of and I am ready to get back into the workforce. I would be open to elaborate more if you have further questions!",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_furloughed:'Due to the ongoing pandemic, my current place of work has furloughed all employees until further notice. As I currently do not have a timeline for returning to work, I’m searching for a new role. As a hardworking <FONT COLOR="#FF6600">[Previous Job Title]</FONT> with a strong record of dedicated service, I know I can be a valuable addition to your team at <FONT COLOR="#FF6600">[Target Company]</FONT>',lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_jobsearch:'On my resume, you will notice a gap in my employment from <FONT COLOR="#FF6600">[Date]</FONT> to <FONT COLOR="#FF6600">[Date]</FONT>. During this time I was weighing my options as to what I wanted to do next, and once I decided that the <FONT COLOR="#FF6600">[Industry]</FONT> industry is where I belong, I began to search for my next role.',lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_laidoff:'In my previous role I was a skilled and hardworking <FONT COLOR="#FF6600">[Previous Job Title]</FONT>, but due to the ongoing pandemic my previous employer was forced to lay off all employees. While this period was unplanned and unexpected, I put the time to good use and am ready to get back to the workforce.',lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_relocation:"As you review my resume, you may notice a brief gap in my work experience. I resigned from my previous position to relocate across country to accommodate a new career opportunity for my spouse. While managing the logistics of my move, I studied industry news, trends and events to keep my knowledge current. I am now settled and prepared to take the next steps in my career.",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_sabbatical:"Upon your evaluation of my resume, you will note a period of time unaccounted for. I elected to pursue a short sabbatical. With full disclosure to my employer, I embarked on a personal mission to enhance my professional experience and knowledge base. I would be open to elaborate more if you have further questions!",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_sickfamily:"As you can see in my resume, I have a gap in my employment history where I was unable to work due to caring for a family member that contracted COVID-19. With my family member having made a full recovery and testing negative for the virus, I’m ready to return to work.",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_sickself:"As you can see in my resume, I have a gap in my employment history where I was unable to work due to contracting COVID-19. Having made a full recovery and tested negative for the virus, I’m ready to return to the workforce.",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_takingcare:"When reviewing my resume, you might notice a gap in employment. My absence is due to me taking time to care for my children.  My child-rearing experience has enhanced my talents in leadership, teamwork, determination, and prioritization as I managed multiple schedules, trained others, enforced rules and provided around-the-clock care. I am now settled and prepared to get back into the workforce.",lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_travel:"In reference to the gap in employment shown on my resume, I capitalized on an opportunity to travel in an effort to gain new experiences, foster personal development, and bring a renewed perspective to my field of study. This period of travel allowed me to build strong connections with other individuals and cultures, which has cultivated new growth and a better understanding of my future goals.",lbl_workgapreason_reason_covid19:"Impacted by pandemic",lbl_workgapreason_reason_education:"Education",lbl_workgapreason_reason_family:"Family / Personal medical issues",lbl_workgapreason_reason_furloughed:"Furloughed",lbl_workgapreason_reason_jobsearch:"Job searching",lbl_workgapreason_reason_laidoff:"Laid off",lbl_workgapreason_reason_relocation:"Relocation",lbl_workgapreason_reason_sabbatical:"Sabbatical",lbl_workgapreason_reason_sickfamily:"Personal reason (Family)",lbl_workgapreason_reason_sickself:"Personal reason (Myself)",lbl_workgapreason_reason_takingcare:"Taking care of children",lbl_workgapreason_reason_travel:"Travel",lbl_modal_title_1:"We detected a gap in your work history",lbl_modal_title_2:"We will generate a cover letter to explain gaps in your work history",lbl_modal_question_1:"Do you have a gap in your work history that you want to explain?",lbl_modal_question_2:"Were you out of work?",lbl_modal_question_3:"How were you affected?",lbl_modal_answer_1:"We can help you generate a cover letter to explain any such gaps",lbl_modal_answer_2:"Choose one reason that best fits your option",lbl_workgapreason_allowed:"Yes",lbl_workgapreason_notallowed:"No",lbl_experiencegap_notification_title:"Work experience gap explained",lbl_sectionList_name_GAPS:"Gaps",lbl_sectionList_name_SIGNATURE:"Signature",lbl_defaultDocCharVal_Subject:"RE: {0}",gaps_sectionCD:a.TypeCodes.sectionTypeCd.Gaps,storageKeys:{JobsList:"JobsList",LatestJob:"LatestJob",GapReason:"GapReason",CustomGapReason:"CustomGapReason",IsImpactedByPandemic:"IsImpactedByPandemic",IsCLGeneratedAndGapExplained:"IsCLGeneratedAndGapExplained",GapsExplainingCoverLetterId:"GapsExplainingCoverLetterId",FourYearGapMonthsInitial:"initial last 4 years career gap",FourYearGapMonthsUpdated:"updated last 4 years career gap",TotalYearGapMonths:"total career gap"},popupVariations:{1:"explain gap with cover letter",2:"explain gap reason",3:"how were you affected"}},tr=[{reason:"lbl_workgapreason_reason_furloughed",paraContent:"lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_furloughed"},{reason:"lbl_workgapreason_reason_laidoff",paraContent:"lbl_workgapreason_paraContent_laidoff"},{re