sheets etc)<br />\\\\n5. Similar duties as needed.<br />\\\\n<br />\\\\nRequirements:<br />\\\\n<br />\\\\n1. 2 years experience working in an office at an assisted living or similar facility.<br />\\\\n2. Warm, friendly, professional demeanor.<br />\\\\n3. Strong typing and computer skills.<br />\\\\n4. Experience with payroll is a plus.<br />\\\\n<br />\\\\nCompensation: $16-$18 per hour plus healthcare and PTO.\\",\\"EmploymentTypeCD\\":\\"\\",\\"HighlightingSnippet\\":null,\\"ID\\":\\"ae3b27198955bb2288abcfe7bf8e9ed9\\",\\"ImageUrl\\":null,\\"IsHighlighted\\":false,\\"JobPulseTitle\\":\\"Front Office Assistant\\",\\"JobScore\\":0,\\"JobTitle\\":\\"Front Office Administrator For Assisted Living\\",\\"Match\\":null,\\"OtherSkills\\":[\\"Assisted Living\\",\\"Customer Service\\",\\"Typing\\",\\"Front Office\\",\\"Administrative Functions\\",\\"Computer Sales\\"],\\"PostalCode\\":\\"92544\\",\\"PUID\\":\\"12949849\\",\\"SalaryEstimate\\":\\"$30.53K\\",\\"Score\\":\\"1\\",\\"SearchProvider\\":null,\\"Source\\":\\"CAR\\",\\"SourceType\\":\\"STORE\\",\\"State\\":\\"CA\\",\\"StatusCD\\":\\"ACTV\\",\\"TitleSkills\\":[{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":false,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Front Office\\"},{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":false,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Customer Service\\"},{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":false,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Customer Billing\\"},{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":false,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Data Entry\\"},{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":false,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Teamwork / Collaboration\\"},{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":true,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Medical Office Experience\\"},{\\"isCritical\\":false,\\"isExpensive\\":false,\\"isHardToFill\\":true,\\"skillOrCertification\\":\\"Customer Checkout\